			<Set Text="Gain 50 [ICON_GOLD] Gold each time a Great Person is expended. Each source of [ICON_RES_MARBLE] Marble or [ICON_RES_STONE] Stone worked by this City produces +2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold."/>
